snippet.title: Yoshi Commits Tax Fraud 64 F3 Trailer (+ Yoshi Direct Announcement!)
snippet.description:
YOSHI DIRECT: 7/15 at 12PM PST/3PM EST https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=guUQVh8DwjQ
Make sure to tune in for an extended look at Yoshi Commits Tax Fraud 64, including a playable demo!

After over a year, the next trailer for Yoshi Commits Tax Fraud 64 has been released! A lot has been incorporated into the game since the previous trailer, so be sure to check it out!

I stream progress on this hack! https://twitch.tv/cheezepin
My server dedicated to this hack: https://discord.gg/5SNhsGF
